		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Some suggested additions to this page :<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Colour-emphasis_games">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Colo ... asis_games</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Final Fantasy - rapidly sets and clears all 3 emphasis bits to flash the screen when going into a battle screen or the menus by pressing start or select.<br /><br />Final Fantasy 2 - rapidly sets and clears uses all 3 emphasis bits to flash the screen<br /><br />Super Spy Hunter - sets all 3 emphasis bits when the game is paused.  The Japanese version, Battle Formula, does not do this.

		

